7:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both HubSpot Operations Hub and Salesforce Flow share a solid foundation of core features including Visual Builder, Code Support, Api Connections, Scheduling. On the other hand, Salesforce Flow uniquely offers Ai Actions, giving it an edge for users who prioritize this area. \n\nLooking at user ratings, HubSpot Operations Hub holds an overall score of 7/10 and an ease of use score of 7/10, while Salesforce Flow scores 7/10 overall and 4/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
8:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, both HubSpot Operations Hub and Salesforce Flow offer flexible pricing models. HubSpot Operations Hub has a notable advantage here with its free plan, allowing you to get started without any financial commitment. Salesforce Flow does not currently offer a free tier, which means you will need to pay from day one."}]]}]
